      "media": [],
      "retweet": null,
      "quoted": {
        "id": "2042964934862979554",
        "text": "Instead of a two-speed transmission, The Tesla Semi has two rear axles.\n\nThe forward axle, with two motors, is geared for acceleration, while the rear axle is geared for highway efficiency. The Semi has a tri-motor setup with 800kW of power. \n\nAt highway speeds, the front axle will completely disengage.",
